                                 BUSINESS QUESTION
How much money is lost through fraudulent transactions? 

                                  QUERY
SELECT
CASE
WHEN fraud = 1 THEN 'total revenue lost'
ELSE 'balance'
END AS Fraud_category,
SUM(amount)
FROM fraud_detection_data
GROUP BY Fraud_category;

                              Insight:
The total revenue the company has lost is 3,822,671.17,which is a great lose to the company
